      "writtenOn": "2026-04-01T10:52:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If operatingConfigInterface fails to initialize, this early return skips makeSensors() and eventReporting-\u003einit(), so the entire GPU device will have no temperature, power, voltage sensors, and no event subscription. The utilization interface failure should not prevent critical sensors from being created. \nConsider continuing without it on failure instead of returning.",
